data.description: Sellers offering $10,000 credit to use towards buyers closing costs or rate buydown. Discover a hidden treasure nestled along Highway 87 in Navarre, where sustainability meets tranquility. Situated on a private 1.01-acre lot, zoned for agriculture, this property unveils a beautifully updated and remodeled home, cocooned by a flourishing garden of vegetables, fruits, and herbs. This turn-key ready home CAN BE sold fully furnished and has been thoughtfully updated throughout. It features 1,869 sq ft of living space, three generously sized bedrooms AND an oversized 20x11 bonus room that can serve as a 4th bedroom, office, den, or playroom. The kitchen has been updated with a spacious single-basin farmhouse sink, new countertops, freshly painted cabinets, metal farmhouse-style backsplash, and all new appliances. The expansive lot is a canvas of limitless possibilities and a haven for animal enthusiasts! Ducks, chickens, rabbits, pigs, donkeys, and goats, have called this place home. Impeccable attention to detail is evident, from well-maintained planter boxes to secure fencing, gates, and latches. The entire lot is fenced to provide the utmost tranquility. The detached workshop with a carport, was recently rewired with all-new electrical, making it ideal for tools, storage, outdoor gear, toys, or working on projects. Beyond its charm, this legendary property has earned recognition for hosting tours, field trips, and gatherings, making it a perfect spot for nature enthusiasts and animal lovers alike. Explore the vast landscape for hiking and fishing just steps away from the property. This Navarre gem offers a rare opportunity to live a sustainable, peaceful, and enriching lifestyle, all while being just a short drive away from shopping, military bases, and the pristine shores of Navarre Beach. Schedule a showing today!
